cs.LG, cs.RO, cs.SY, cs.AI, cs.NE 

This paper proposes a policy initialization algorithm for reinforcement learning, which involves the use of neural networks and multi-parametric programming. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.RO (Robotics), as the paper discusses the application of the proposed algorithm in controlling agents and environments. The paper also involves the use of control theory, which suggests the possibility of cs.SY (Systems and Control) as a sub-category. Additionally, the paper involves the use of artificial intelligence techniques, which suggests the possibility of cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) as sub-categories.
